title.narrative: Multitranche Financing Facility (MFF) - Gansu Heihe Rural Hydropower Development Investment Program - Project 2: Dagushan Hydropower Project

description.narrative: The Investment Program will finance the construction of 2 medium-sized hydropower plants (HPPs) in the Heihe river cascade hydropwoer development scheme. The Investment Program's main impact will be to provide environmentally clean power supply in rural areas of Gansu Province.
